  "remarks": "TAi.015 Title: Mullah. Designation: Minister of Communication under the Taliban regime. Member of the Taliban Supreme Council as at 2009. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Nurzai tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 23 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 January 2001 (amended on 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov. 2011)",
